1
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:19,040
However,

2
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:22,840
Brother Shiqi does seem to have gotten more handsome.

3
00:00:23,880 --> 00:00:24,880
And stronger too.

4
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,200
Why am I itching all over?

5
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:00,600
Brother Shiqi.

6
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,840
Brother Shiqi.

7
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,120
Rest assured.

8
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:16,120
I have asked the Warlord to investigate thoroughly.

9
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,980
He didn't return from the Song residence all night.

10
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,740
He will definitely give you an explanation.

11
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:24,400
The Warlord was at the Song residence

12
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,000
all night.

13
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,840
With his lack of courage,

14
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,720
he wouldn't dare cause any trouble.

15
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:29,480
Don't worry.

16
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,600
How is it?

17
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,200
Did you get an answer?

18
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:51,039
You're quite good at acting.

19
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,479
I have

20
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,020
investigated carefully.

21
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,400
What Song Wencai did

22
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,000
has absolutely nothing to do

23
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,530
with his father, Song Ping.

24
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,240
You are all just

25
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,560
chasing shadows

26
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,240
and making wild guesses.

27
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,880
Mayor Su.

28
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,520
As mayor,

29
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:11,200
if you are still so foolish,

30
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,560
then someone else

31
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,300
should take this seat.

32
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,640
What's wrong with you?

33
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,400
Is this the result of your interrogation?

34
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,680
Did you not understand what I said?

35
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,480
Shut up.

36
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:24,240
When men are talking,

37
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,920
women shouldn't interrupt.

38
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,120
I am the military governor,

39
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,240
not your lackey.

40
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:31,480
Don't think just because your brother is the marshal

41
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:33,600
you can do whatever you want in front of me.

42
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,400
Be careful, or I won't hold back.

43
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,480
Madam.

44
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:59,120
There is something wrong with the Warlord.

45
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,600
Right.

46
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,480
The Warlord's attitude towards Madam

47
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:03,600
is completely different from yesterday.

48
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,600
Could the Warlord

49
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,800
have been cursed

50
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,380
in the Song residence?

51
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,120
Enough.

52
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,760
Stop talking.

53
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,980
How dare you discuss the Warlord?

54
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,800
Men

55
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,770
are just like children sometimes.

56
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:23,370
It is normal to lose temper occasionally.

57
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:25,200
Song Ping is his relative.

58
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:27,000
It's hard for him not to take his side.

59
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,730
A man who really cares about you

60
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,760
will know when to stop.

61
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,079
When you get married in the future,

62
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,410
you must remember this.

63
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,680
This is the only way

64
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,329
to control a man.

65
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,440
Don't you think it's strange?

66
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,280
Overnight,

67
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,040
without warning,

68
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,160
it just changed.

69
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,200
Madam.

70
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,400
Madam.

71
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,200
Madam.

72
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,460
Brother Shiqi.

73
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,530
Someone put sleeping pills

74
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,720
in your teacup.

75
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:48,640
Sleeping pills?

76
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,000
Yes.

77
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,280
Who did it?

78
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:51,760
It was me.

79
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,560
Didn't you say

80
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:01,280
you always have trouble sleeping?

81
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:03,680
I specifically asked Song Ping to prepare some sleeping pills

82
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,680
to help you sleep.

83
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,320
It's so late.

84
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,000
Why is he here?

85
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,520
Wang Shiqi.

86
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:15,440
It's bad enough that you usually fool around outside

87
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:17,360
and mess with so many women.

88
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,400
How could you take advantage of the Warlord's absence

89
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:20,640
and sneak into Madam's room?

90
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,800
If word gets out,

91
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,600
how will the Warlord save face?

92
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,120
Chief Song,

93
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,570
why did you suddenly become so righteous?

94
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,240
It makes me a bit uncomfortable.

95
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,200
I advise you to go back to

96
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:34,060
being despicable and shameless.

97
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,200
Brother Shiqi felt something was wrong

98
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,130
and got worried,

99
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,300
so he came to check.

100
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:42,080
I think you're the ones acting suspicious.

101
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:44,200
Ever since you arrived at Taohua Town,

102
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:46,000
you two have been flirting with each other.

103
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,680
Exactly.

104
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,640
Dalang,

105
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:50,170
Brother Shiqi and I are not what you think.

106
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,930
Are you treating me like a fool?

107
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,320
Governor,

108
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,400
the innocent will be proven innocent.

109
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:58,800
Some people have been doing dirty tricks behind our backs.

110
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,860
Everyone knows it.

111
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,320
Who do you think you are

112
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:04,080
to meddle in our marital affairs?

113
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:05,840
I don't care about your marital affairs.

114
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,900
But let me tell you,

115
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,600
if you dare to bully Madam,

116
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,080
even if you are the Military Governor,

117
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,280
I will never let you get away with it.

118
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:11,760
You!

119
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,240
Dalang!

120
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:16,960
Dalang!

121
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,120
What's wrong, Dalang?

122
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,320
Are you okay, Dalang?

123
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,200
Wang Shiqi.

124
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,840
Look how mad you've made the Military Governor!

125
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:22,760
My head.

126
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,460
It hurts like it's splitting!

127
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:25,960
Madam.

128
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,680
Get out.

129
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,200
Get lost.

130
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,240
Shiqi.

131
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,520
You'd better go.

132
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,460
This is between my husband and me.

133
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,730
We don't need you to interfere.

134
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,200
I don't want him to misunderstand again.

135
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:39,200
Leave now.

136
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:40,320
Get out.

137
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,200
Go.

138
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,260
Hurry up and leave.

139
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,800
You have quite a temper.

140
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,640
Back when we were at war,

141
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,600
I didn't even see you this agitated.

142
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,520
My lady,

143
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:02,240
considering we have been husband and wife

144
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,400
for seven years,

145
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,840
and have even

146
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,080
gone through life and death together,

147
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:09,440
can you stop seeing that Wang Shiqi?

148
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,360
Ever since you met him,

149
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,200
nothing has been right.

150
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,200
Just take your medicine first, Dalang.

151
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,060
What are you doing?

152
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,800
Do you really want me to die?

153
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,080
Okay, okay.

154
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,980
I'll do whatever you want,

155
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,800
okay?

156
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,040
Lie down.

157
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,520
You finally came back.

158
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:30,680
Dalang.

159
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,360
Dalang.

160
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,840
Dalang.
